    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cbd6252b8057acd2cd41a70"
      },
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Count von Steffelbus, how are you certain they were operating with the Combine?\n\nWe are very far from my family's country and the [[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreRimwardPeriphery],Rimward Periphery]] is crawling with criminals and impersonators.",
      "branches": [
