    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c15efcdeda6b3608575c0af"
      },
      "index": 2,
      "text": "I had expected the wrath of the 'Dragon' for attempting to interfere on their success, if I had tried to replicate the <i>[[DM.BaseDescriptionDefs[LoreHolovidTheAttackOfThePolymerCoatedMan],The Attack of the Polymer-Coated Man]]</i> in a world close to Kurita space.\n\nMy mistake was expecting that I could avoid their ISF spies by moving to the other side of the galaxy.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 3,
